<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">Velvet scoter</span></h1>
<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
<div id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</div>
<div id="contentSub">  (Redirected from <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Melanitta_fusca&amp;redirect=no" title="Melanitta fusca">Melanitta fusca</a>)</div>
